description:
Hannah Bronfman, the DJ, fitness influencer, and beauty entrepreneur is here to help us recalibrate for the new year. She opens up her beauty black book, reveals what's on her top shelf, and predicts that persimmons will be the It fruit of 2019. Before that: a tribute to Oribe Canales, our favorite holiday candles, and how to treat broken blood vessels on your face.
